Natural: What is the number of fields of paper with title 'Natural Language Processing'?
SQL: SELECT DISTINCT COUNT(*) FROM FieldID_Topic JOIN PaperID_FieldID ON FieldID_Topic.FieldID=PaperID_FieldID.FieldID JOIN PaperID_Title on PaperID_FieldID.PaperID=PaperID_Title.PaperID WHERE PaperID_Title.Title='Natural Language Processing'

Natural: What is the number of papers published on and after an year 1982?
SQL: SELECT DISTINCT COUNT(*) FROM PaperID_Title JOIN ConfID_PaperID ON ConfID_PaperID.PaperID=PaperID_Title.PaperID JOIN ConfID_Venue_Year ON ConfID_Venue_Year.ConfID=ConfID_PaperID.ConfID WHERE ConfID_Venue_Year.Year='1982'

Natural: Show the papers published on and after an year 1992
SQL: SELECT DISTINCT PaperID_Title.Title FROM PaperID_Title JOIN ConfID_PaperID ON ConfID_PaperID.PaperID=PaperID_Title.PaperID JOIN ConfID_Venue_Year ON ConfID_Venue_Year.ConfID=ConfID_PaperID.ConfID WHERE ConfID_Venue_Year.Year >= '1992'

Natural: Display all the papers published in the year 2002 at 'Venue'

Natural: Display all the conference venue on field 'Word Segmentation' in year Year
SQL: SELECT DISTINCT ConfID_Venue_Year.Venue FROM ConfID_Venue_Year JOIN ConfID_FieldID ON ConfID_Venue_Year.ConfID=ConfID_FieldID.ConfID JOIN FieldID_Topic ON ConfID_FieldID.FieldID=FieldID_Topic.FieldID Where FieldID_Topic.Topic Like 'Word Segmentation' and ConfID_Venue_Year.Year='Year'
